OL,3,CPrison death of hotel rioter to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated over mental health
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FThe death of a grandfather in prison
OL,8,Ffor rioting outside a hotel housing
OL,9,Fasylum seekers is to be investigated,
OL,10,Fafter concerns were raised about
OL,11,F"missed opportunities" to support him.
OL,13,FPeter Lynch died at HMP Moorland in
OL,14,FSouth Yorkshire where he was serving a
OL,15,Fsentence for his part in the disorder
OL,16,Foutside a Holiday Inn Express in
OL,17,FRotherham in the summer of 2024.
OL,19,FThe 61-year-old died in October that
OL,20,Fyear from hanging.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
