PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778861473
OL,3,CPrison death of hotel rioter to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated over mental health
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FIssues have since been raised over Mr
OL,8,FLynch's mental health and relevant
OL,9,Fassessments, which will now be looked
OL,10,Finto in a full jury inquest.
OL,12,FA pre-inquest review held at Doncaster
OL,13,FCoroner's Court on Thursday outlined
OL,14,Fthat a full hearing was to take place
OL,15,Fin July outlining the full 10 week
OL,16,Fperiod between Mr Lynch's initial
OL,17,Farrest, his detention by South
OL,18,FYorkshire Police, and his days spent
OL,19,Fat HMP Doncaster and subsequently HMP
OL,20,FMoorland.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778861473
OL,3,CPrison death of hotel rioter to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated over mental health
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FCoroner Nicola Mundy said July's
OL,8,Fhearing would cover a range of areas,
OL,9,Fincluding matters which may have
OL,10,Fimpacted on his mental health, whether
OL,11,Fthere was any evidence of increased
OL,12,Fvulnerability, and whether there were
OL,13,Fany missed opportunities to put
OL,14,Ffurther support in place.
OL,16,FA previous hearing into Mr Lynch's
OL,17,Fdeath heard he had been accused of
OL,18,Fbreaking prison rules at the time of
OL,19,Fhis death, although Mrs Mundy said on
OL,20,FThursday that the inquest's purpose
OL,21,Fwas not to determine his guilt.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778861473
OL,3,CPrison death of hotel rioter to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated over mental health
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FShe did however say this allegation
OL,8,Fmay have been a "potentially
OL,9,Fsignificant event" and would be fully
OL,10,Finvestigated in the hearing over the
OL,11,Fsummer.
OL,13,FShe stressed: "I will not be
OL,14,Fcriticising in any way judgments of
OL,15,Fother courts."
OL,26,@uD@OOUwD@NO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
