PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778861473
OL,3,CPrison death of hotel rioter to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated over mental health
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FMr Lynch was arrested on August 4
OL,8,Foutside the hotel, where he had been
OL,9,Fcaptured on police body cameras waving
OL,10,Fa conspiracy theory placard,
OL,11,Fscreaming, "you are protecting people
OL,12,Fwho are killing our kids and raping
OL,13,Fthem" and "scum" at officers with riot
OL,14,Fshields.
OL,16,FHis conviction was one of more than
OL,17,F100 at Sheffield Crown Court for the
OL,18,Fdisorder, sparked by misinformation
OL,19,Fabout the identity of a teenager
OL,20,Farrested over the attacks on a dance
OL,21,Fclass in Southport.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
