OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778861473
OL,3,CPrison death of hotel rioter to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated over mental health
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FRiots outside the Rotherham hotel left
OL,8,F64 police officers, four police dogs
OL,9,Fand a horse injured.
OL,11,FMr Lynch, from Wath-upon-Dearne,
OL,12,FRotherham, had suffered from diabetes,
OL,13,Fthyroid issues and heart problems,
OL,14,FSheffield Crown Court had heard at the
OL,15,Ftime of his sentencing.
OL,17,FHe had also been married for 36 years
OL,18,Fand had four adult children and three
OL,19,Fgrandchildren.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
