PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778861473
OL,3,CPrison death of hotel rioter to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated over mental health
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FSome of his family were in court for
OL,8,FThursday's pre-inquest review and
OL,9,Fanother family member joined by
OL,10,Fvideolink.The coroner said the inquest
OL,11,Fwill start on July 20 and is currently
OL,12,Fscheduled to finish on August 4.
